  "instructions": [
    "1. Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high.",
    "2. Add chicken; cook until browned, about 5-7 minutes.",
    "3. Add onion, garlic, and smoky paprika; cook until onion is translucent, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "4. Add stew tomatoes, chicken broth, salt, and pepper.",
    "5. Bring to a boil; reduce heat to medium-low and simmer, covered, for 20-25 minutes.",
    "6. Stir in chopped crisp lettuce.",
    "7. Serve hot, garnished with additional crisp lettuce if desired."
